じぇ！『あまちゃん』サントラ異例の5位　朝ドラ初のTOP10入り</span> |publisher=[[Oricon|Oricon]] |date=2013-06-25 |accessdate=2013-08-12 |archive-date=2013-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731044750/http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/rankmusic/2025947/full |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《小海女》原聲帶專輯的首星期銷量為上年同時期的《[[小梅醫生|小梅醫生]]》（約2,500張）的六倍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.daily.co.jp/gossip/2013/06/08/0006058501.shtml |language=ja |title=<span lang="ja">「あまちゃん」サントラ発売前注文殺到</span> |publisher=Daily Sports Online |date=2013-06-08 |accessdate=2013-08-12 |archive-date=2013-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730032044/http://www.daily.co.jp/gossip/2013/06/08/0006058501.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

